Quamquam seems to imply that Laelius did not altogether agree with Scipi0.on this subject. — expediret: sc. utrique. — sentiretur: sc. ab utroque. — saepe: probably to be taken with mutari, not with dicebat, so that alias. ..alias is an expansion or explanation of saepe.
